<div>
	<h1>Tic-Tac-Toe</h1>
	<p>Welcome to Tic-Tac-Toe! This is a two player game. Each player takes turns marking X or O in one of the boxes on the game board until one player has three in a row (horizontally, vertically, or diagonally) or until there are no more availalbe moves. Good luck!</p>

	<button id='new-game-button'>New Game</button>
	<button id='undo-button'>Undo</button>

	<div id='game-board'>
		<div class='row'>
			<div class='cell player-0' id='0-0'></div>
			<div class='cell player-0' id='0-1'></div>
			<div class='cell player-0' id='0-2'></div>
		</div>
		<div class='row'>
			<div class='cell player-0' id='1-0'></div>
			<div class='cell player-0' id='1-1'></div>
			<div class='cell player-0' id='1-2'></div>
		</div>
		<div class='row'>
			<div class='cell player-0' id='2-0'></div>
			<div class='cell player-0' id='2-1'></div>
			<div class='cell player-0' id='2-2'></div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>